  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <div rend="parallel">
        <p xml:id="Aink287-kilavi">iṉṉanāḷil varaival eṉak kūṟi annāḷil varaiyātu piṉ avvāṟu kūṟum talaimakaṟkut tōḻi kūṟiyatu.
           </p>
        <p xml:lang="en"> What the confidante said to the hero, who had said, “I will marry [her] on such-and-such a day,” but did not marry [her] on that day, and later spoke again in the same way.</p>
      </div>
      <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink287">
<l>neṭuvarai micaiyatu kuṟuṅkāl varuṭai</l>
<l>tiṉaipāy kiḷḷai verūu nāṭa</l>
<l>vallai maṉṟa poyttal</l>
<l>vallāy maṉṟanī yallatu ceyalē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
        <l>O man from the land where parakeets that pervade the millet fields</l>
        <l>fear the short-legged mountain sheep on the summit of the high hills,</l>
        <l>you are indeed capable of lying—</l>
        <l>but you are certainly incapable of doing what is improper.</l>
        
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
